  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized trial investigating the use of the IMPELLA RECOVER LP 2.5 compared to
      Intra-aortic balloon pump (IABP) in patients with Acute Myocardial Infarction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
